Generic single-database configuration.

# ðŸ“¦ Database Setup

## Criar schema inicial
```bash
psql -U postgres -d assistant_db -f database/schema.sql
```

### Popular com dados de exemplo
```
psql -U postgres -d assistant_db -f database/seed.sql
```

## Usar Alembic
```
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "create feedbacks table"
alembic upgrade head
```

